author: Theresa Geteles (noreply@blogger.com)
text:
Russian black/death metal warriors FREIHEIT have posted "Технократия", a track from the bands anticipated new release "Безумие. Ненависть. Смерть", due to be unleashed 5/5/2017 via GRIMM DISTRIBUTION and SATANATH RECORDS (CO-RELEASE). FREIHEIT unleashed "FREIHEIT" (EP), 5/18/2016 (SELF RELEASED). 

FROM GRIMM DISTRIBUTION: 
Freiheit new song! 

FROM FREIHEIT: 
Release by our label-partner GrimmDistribution (Belarus) - new album "Безумие. Ненависть. Смерть" of Russian black/death metal band Freiheit out on May 5th, 2017!

Format: Jewel case CD, 500 copies

Catalog number: 006GD

http://vk.com/freiheitband 
http://www.facebook.com/freiheitband 
http://soundcloud.com/freiheit-band 
http://grimmdistribution.bandcamp.com...
